# mcp-SERVICE_NAME

SERVICE_DESCRIPTION

## Setup

### Prerequisites
- Node.js 18+

### Environment Variables

| Variable | Required | Description |
|----------|----------|-------------|
| `SERVICE_API_KEY` | Yes | Your API key from SERVICE_PROVIDER |

### Installation

**As a Claude Code plugin:**
```bash
claude --plugin-dir /path/to/mcp-SERVICE_NAME
```

**Or add to a marketplace and install:**
```bash
/plugin install mcp-SERVICE_NAME@marketplace-name
```

### Manual setup
```bash
cd mcp-SERVICE_NAME
npm install
```

